* FogBugz Command Line Interface

Install with:

    $> python setup.py install

Run with:

    $> fb
    $> fb --logging=debug  # verbose
    $> fb --help  # for more options

Get help from `fb`:

    >>> help

Based on:

    http://help.fogcreek.com/8202/xml-api

* Development

Run tests with:

   >>> python setup.py test

* References

    https://developers.fogbugz.com/?W199
    https://developers.fogbugz.com/default.asp?W194#toc_4
    http://help.fogcreek.com/8202/xml-api#Sample_XML_Payloads

